    "description": {
      "content": "The TIAA Secure Income Account (SIA) API enables recordkeepers and plan administrators to integrate TIAA's guaranteed lifetime income product into custom target-date model portfolios and managed account solutions. The SIA API supports participant account setup, contribution management, allocation updates, and income projection calculations for defined contribution plans. Authentication uses OAuth 2.0 Client Credentials Flow.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: TIAA Developer Support",
